A Studio Ghibli style illustration of two young twin toddlers sitting side by side on a soft grassy hill, both with identical mischievous grins and sparkling eyes, their expressions full of playful conspiracy. Warm golden afternoon sunlight bathes the scene, casting long gentle shadows. Behind them, a whimsical garden with oversized flowers and curious butterflies. The twins wear simple matching outfits in soft pastel colors. Their body language suggests they just shared a secret joke. Soft watercolor textures, dreamy atmosphere, gentle wind rustling their hair, capturing pure childhood joy and the special bond between siblings.
